overview.en: Entertainment King community is mainly committed to building a global sports and entertainment community. YLTWB token is used to motivate community members who contribute to the community and enhance their enthusiasm for sports and entertainment
overview.zh: 娱乐天王社区主要致力于建设一个全球的运动娱乐社区，YLTWB Token用于激励为社区做出贡献的社区成员，提升大家运动娱乐积极性
